spec_data.Name: NetworkManager-libnm-devel
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the header and pkg-config files for development
applications using NetworkManager functionality from applications.  This
is the new NetworkManager API. See also NetworkManager-glib-devel.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 17 Nov 2017 05:22:39 PM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Header files for adding NetworkManager support to applications (new API).
